dct_description_sm: Inset map: Hôtel de Ville district. Map shows arrondissement boundary, autobus roads, trolleybus, and tramway lines. Oriented with north toward the upper left. Includes index to points of interest and public buildings; principal churches; museums and monuments; education; hospitals and social services; parks and sports; and stations of transportation.
